name: Dark_Ocean_Bloodmoon_edit_by_0110
description: @tekknovator | The sky darkened and the moon turned red, turning the water into an oily surface, it's existence only given away by the blood red reflections of the light. Without light, it would not be visible. Space would be invisible. Space would be non existent. Without the moon, time would be impossible to see, time would not exist without the moonlight.
